General.Name: Todd River Resources Ltd
General.Description: Todd River Resources Limited engages in mineral exploration and evaluation company in Australia. It holds 100% interest in various projects, including the Berkshire Valley Project located in the South West Yilgarn Craton; PINGRUP Ni-Cu-PGE Project covering an area of 240 square kilometers located in the south west Yilgarn Craton"Youanmi Terrane; Mount Hardy Project located in the northern territory; Petermanns Project; Bangemall Project located in the south of Paraburdoo; McArthur Project covering an area of 450 kilometers located in the south-east of Katherine; and Nerramyne Copper Project located to the northeast of Geraldton in Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2014 is based in Subiaco, Australia.
